            169.87777709960938
          ],
          "text": "RBI/DCM/2018-19/62 \nMaster Direction DCM (CC) No. G - 5/03.35.01/2018-19 \n     July 3, 2018",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
